{"tid":633803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［巴打入］鍾意異性點樣嗲你","createTime":"2018-04-18T15:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T04:35:23.000Z","uid":63521,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"76d2d405d9d939d7fc411ce8ce56897c38c92f33","tid":633803,"uid":63521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:29:33.000Z","msg":"有啲女仔天生唔係好識嗲人 <br />\n我就係其中一個好例子<br />\n個個唔識睇樣以為我好斯文成日嗲人個啲<br />\n實則就係男人婆咁 粗粗魯魯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好聽啲講叫爽朗 不過如果可以識番少少嗲好似會更好<br />\n想知男仔鍾意女仔點嗲你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名學野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ffd10c8a20072d28ca49d7754398b79737c303","tid":633803,"uid":149357,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"我都唔識嗲人 但係我發現<br />\n到遇到鍾意既人 自然識嗲佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9e24ec6c8243bd4871f0028886c78f01094d86","tid":633803,"uid":85557,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"耶!好衰架，射到人成身都係，一陣比人插返阿。"},{"pid":"7e45619ea07510236404f0a66b1415619bc1bc6c","tid":633803,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"跪低含佢條撚"},{"pid":"60253798d69267bbb0fad9170a039706746bd393","tid":633803,"uid":63521,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"有無正常啲嘅答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd085a6a3b86c9857b4118da9e8172dbe67d711","tid":633803,"uid":77769,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score